          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Military Retirement Credit for Distance Learning Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows a credit of up to 10 points toward computation of years of service for retired pay upon successful completion of a course of instruction using electronically delivered methodologies to accomplish military education or training.</p>]]></text>
